20. How to list all files, including hidden ones, in a directory?
#ls -al

21. How to add a new system user without login permissions?
#adduser subversion --shell=/bin/false --no-create-home

22. Explain a hardlink. What happens when a hardlink is removed?
#Hard links point directly to the physical file on disk, and not on the path name. 
This means that if you rename or move the original file, the link will not break, 
since the link is for the file itself, not the path where the file is located.

23. What happens when a sysadmin executes this command: chmod 444 chmod
# $ cp -p /usr/bin/grep /tmp/testfile
$ cat /usr/bin/chmod > /tmp/testfile
$ cp -p /tmp/testfile /usr/bin/chmod

